```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Start: alma_multiply] --> B{n <= 256?}
    B -->|Yes| C[Single BLAS dgemm]
    B -->|No| D[Allocate metadata arrays]
    D --> E[Classify all blocks]
    E --> F[Initialize C to zero]
    F --> G[Parallel block multiply]
    G --> H[For each block pair]
    H --> I[dgemm accumulation]
    I --> J[Free metadata]
    J --> K[End]
    C --> K
```

```mermaid
classDiagram
    class BlockMeta {
        +BlockType type
        +int rows
        +int cols
        +int rank_est
        +int ld
    }

    class MatrixBlock {
        +double* data
        +BlockMeta meta
    }

    class BlockType {
        <<enumeration>>
        LowRank
        Dense
    }

    MatrixBlock --> BlockMeta
    BlockMeta --> BlockType
```

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Main
    participant Alma
    participant BLAS
    participant OpenMP

    Main->>Alma: alma_multiply(A, B, C, n, blockSize)
    
    alt n <= 256
        Alma->>BLAS: cblas_dgemm
        BLAS-->>Alma: result
    else n > 256
        Alma->>Alma: classify_all_blocks(A)
        Alma->>Alma: classify_all_blocks(B)
        Alma->>OpenMP: parallel for initialization
        OpenMP-->>Alma: C initialized
        Alma->>OpenMP: parallel for block multiply
        loop For each block
            OpenMP->>BLAS: cblas_dgemm(block)
            BLAS-->>OpenMP: partial result
        end
        OpenMP-->>Alma: C complete
    end
    
    Alma-->>Main: done
```
